casebody.data:
No. 10-9703 (10A950). Eric John King, Petitioner v. Arizona. 563 U.S. 914, 131 S. Ct. 1811,

179 L. Ed. 2d 673,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2595. March 29, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Arizona, Maricopa County, denied.
